Readings: DevOps
Devops is includes a business model that is widely considered to be a marriage of two competitive departments, development and operations. Collaboration of the two is the main goal. Devops is a culture shift where everyone is aligned towards the same goals, and everyone understands their role in the process towards one common goal. DevOps puts information technology and specifically software and website development at the core of the business. DevOps stems from Agile principles that were adopted when enterprises businesses realized that the waterfall processes werenâ€™t always the best for a workflow. 
